  add(1,6,'1st Lord in 6th House','The 1st house lord in the 6th house ties the self to competition, service, and overcoming obstacles. The native is hardworking, resilient, and thrives in challenging environments. They may excel in service-oriented fields (e.g., healthcare, law) or defeat enemies through determination. Health may be a concern, requiring effort to maintain.',['Health challenges possible','Strong fighting spirit','Service-oriented career','Overcoming debts and enemies','Resilience builds strength']);
  add(1,7,'1st Lord in 7th House','The 1st house lord in the 7th house connects the self to partnerships, marriage, and public dealings. The native\'s identity is heavily influenced by their spouse or business partners, and they thrive in collaborative environments. They are charming, diplomatic, and often successful in relationships or trade.',['Good marriage prospects','Charming personality','Business success through partnerships','Foreign travel possible','Public popularity']);
