  add(1,11,'1st Lord in 11th House','The 1st house lord in the 11th house connects the self to gains, ambitions, and social networks. The native is goal-oriented, socially active, and achieves desires through teamwork or friendships. Their identity is tied to fulfilling aspirations.',['High income and gains','Desires and ambitions fulfilled','Influential social network','Elder sibling support','Multiple income streams']);
